  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69bd02131c3a7f8f360882f9",
      "text": "八卦",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1773994524,
      "updated": 1773994524
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd021b0000000000dca7ce",
      "text": "[八卦 - Wikipedia https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%85%AB%E5%8D%A6]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1773994524,
      "updated": 1773994524
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd021c0000000000dca7cf",
      "text": " > 八卦（はっけ、はっか）は、古代中国から伝わる易における8つの概念のことである。すなわち、一般的な周易では",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1773994524,
      "updated": 1773994540
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd022b0000000000dca7da",
      "text": " > [☰]（乾）",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1773994540,
      "updated": 1773994577
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd022b0000000000dca7db",
      "text": " > ☱（兌）",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1773994540,
      "updated": 1773994540
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd022b0000000000dca7dc",
      "text": " > [☲]（離）",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1773994540,
      "updated": 1773994552
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd022b0000000000dca7dd",
      "text": " > ☳（震）",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1773994540,
      "updated": 1773994540
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd022b0000000000dca7de",
      "text": " > ☴（巽）",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1773994540,
      "updated": 1773994540
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd022b0000000000dca7df",
      "text": " > ☵（坎）",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1773994540,
      "updated": 1773994540
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd022b0000000000dca7e0",
      "text": " > ☶（艮）",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1773994540,
      "updated": 1773994540
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd022b0000000000dca7e1",
      "text": " > ☷（坤）",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1773994540,
      "updated": 1773994540
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd022b0000000000dca7e2",
      "text": " > の八つの卦のことである。以下は、一般的な周易の八卦について主に記し、末尾に香港で使われる連山易・帰蔵易の八卦について記す。",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1773994540,
      "updated": 1773994540
    }
  ]
}